body:
- temporary workaround for background optimizations
- fix bugs with alarm volume (thanks @ajayyy)
- alarms re-enable when setting time (thanks @raboof)
- support for more internet radio sources (@raboof)
- prevent alarms from appearing in recent apps
- updated Chinese translations (thanks @yzqzss)

- prevent issues renaming alarms on some devices (thanks @quipri)
- fix errors in about section, again
- Hungarian localization (thanks @meskobalazs)

- get alarms from local files (thanks @quipri)
- add (some) alarm intents for external applications
- fix errors in about section - #47 
- French localization (thanks @Larnicone)
- Czech localization (thanks @ikanakova)
- Simplified Chinese localization (thanks @yzqzss)

- add alarm intents for external applications
- various bug fixes / performance improvements
- fix errors in about section

- core functionality actually works now; #25
- fixed stopwatch reset bugs; #38
- display scheduled alarm times; #35
- fix theming issues; #39

- changed slow wake-up and sleep reminder units (now stored in seconds)
- increased alarm expansion touch area
- alarm names are now (finally) editable

- fix: inconsistent time when creating alarms
- improved sunrise/sunset theme scheduler
- minor design changes

- new alarm snooze/dismiss layout (#18, #21)
- fixed incompatibility with Android P (#19)
- fixed bugs in time zone dialog

- Spanish translations by @pablomeza10 
- Portuguese translations by @Suburbanno 
- Theming improvements
- Fixed minor time zone-related bugs (#4 and #15)
- Dependency updates

- fixed the fish issue #11 
- the option to "show background image on alarms/timers" actually does something now
- added an empty state, thanks to @rohitkparida
- fixed random crash associated with timers and lifecycle states (commit 0291605)
- improved alarm expand/collapse animations
- German translations by @FriederZi
